Board Meeting Video

Watch the Board of Supervisors meeting live:

  • Live Video Feed (To view the video feed with the agenda, please click on the "In Progress," link below when the meeting is in session. Please note that Internet Explorer is not a supported browser.)
  • Vimeo Livestream
  • YouTube (Closed Captioning available through YouTube)
  • Facebook
  • Twitter
  • Or listen to the live meeting by dialing (619) 531-4716 while business is being conducted. This is a live, listen-only feed.

If you have problems accessing the Board of Supervisors meeting, contact us.

Helpful links for information related to Board of Supervisors meetings:

  • Meeting Calendar
  • Agendas (including supporting documentation and instructions on how to speak at the meeting)
  • Search official Board of Supervisors Records
  • Statements of Proceedings (minutes)
  • Email to order DVD copies of Board meetings.
